<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="id">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
  <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
  <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@tailwindcss/browser@4"></script>
  <script>
    tailwind.config = {
      theme: {
        extend: {
          colors: {
            greenSoft: '#F0F8F0'
          }
        }
      },
      daisyui: {
        themes: ["light"] // Nonaktifkan dark mode
      }
    };
  </script>
  <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/daisyui@3.8.0/dist/full.css" rel="stylesheet">
  <title>FAQ - Portal Alumni FTI</title>
</head>
<body class="bg-greenSoft min-h-screen">

  <!-- Navbar -->
  <div class="navbar bg-white shadow-md px-6">
    <div class="flex justify-between items-center w-full">
      <a class="font-bold text-green-700 text-lg">Portal Alumni FTI</a>
      <ul class="menu menu-horizontal text-black text-sm">
        <li><a href="#" class="nav-item rounded-md px-3 py-1">Beranda</a></li>
        <li><a href="#" class="nav-item rounded-md px-3 py-1">Profil Alumni</a></l>
        <li><a href="#" class="nav-item rounded-md px-3 py-1">Lowongan Pekerjaan</a></li>
        <li><a href="#" class="nav-item rounded-md px-3 py-1">Informasi</a></li>
        <li><a href="#" class="nav-item rounded-md px-3 py-1">Login</a></li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Section: FAQ -->
  <section class="mt-20 py-10 px-4 max-w-4xl mx-auto">
    <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-center text-green-700 mb-10">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>

    <!-- FAQ Card -->
    <div class="space-y-4">

      <!-- Item 1 -->
      <div class="collapse collapse-arrow bg-white shadow rounded-box">
        <input type="checkbox" />
        <div class="collapse-title text-md font-medium text-green-600">
          Bagaimana cara mendaftar sebagai alumni?
        </div>
        <div class="collapse-content text-sm text-gray-700">
          <p>Anda dapat mendaftar melalui halaman pendaftaran dan mengisi data pribadi serta informasi kelulusan Anda.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Item 2 -->
      <div class="collapse collapse-arrow bg-white shadow rounded-box">
        <input type="checkbox" />
        <div class="collapse-title text-md font-medium text-green-600">
          Apakah saya bisa mengajukan lowongan pekerjaan?
        </div>
        <div class="collapse-content text-sm text-gray-700">
          <p>Ya, alumni dapat mengajukan lowongan melalui tombol "Ajukan Lowongan" di halaman lowongan pekerjaan.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Item 3 -->
      <div class="collapse collapse-arrow bg-white shadow rounded-box">
        <input type="checkbox" />
        <div class="collapse-title text-md font-medium text-green-600">
          Bagaimana cara mengubah informasi profil?
        </div>
        <div class="collapse-content text-sm text-gray-700">
          <p>Silakan login terlebih dahulu, lalu kunjungi halaman profil Anda dan klik tombol "Edit".</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Item 4 -->
      <div class="collapse collapse-arrow bg-white shadow rounded-box">
        <input type="checkbox" />
        <div class="collapse-title text-md font-medium text-green-600">
          Apakah saya bisa melihat data alumni lainnya?
        </div>
        <div class="collapse-content text-sm text-gray-700">
          <p>Ya, Anda dapat melihat daftar alumni yang telah mempublikasikan profil mereka secara terbuka.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
    
  </section>

</body>
</html>
